Title: Around the world
DateModified: '2018-02-01'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/around-the-world
SetInCountry: Colombia
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Olga Garcia
AuthorCountry: Canada
Text: A country of many flavours, magical landscapes and warm people.  where the unexpected
  is the norm and beauty is presented in many forms, a culture that  encourage connections
  and sincere smiles. Come and explore fort cities, lost cities... vibrant cities.
  Expose your senses to the music, food and tradition. Be amaze by your finds and
  continue your search because there is always more; the peace of natural landscapes,
  the exiliration of deep connections to people and their environment. From  the Cartagena
  coast to the amazons jungle and the coffee and flower region in between , Colombia
  has so much beauty to share with the world! The seven shades of blues in our oceans
  the never seen before fruits, the richness of its coffee and the unparalleled welcoming
  culture -a piece of paradise to be discovered
